prompts.frontCover: Vibrant comic book style art for a greeting card front. A dynamic, split-panel scene on a cute, tropical beach. In the top panel, a cartoon character of the woman, dressed in a stylish sundress, stands heroically on the sand, holding up a giant boba tea like a trophy. She has a joyful, triumphant expression. A large, stylized comic book sound effect bubble next to her says "SLUUURP!". The background features a turquoise ocean and palm trees. In the bottom panel, a cartoon character of the man, wearing a casual t-shirt and shorts, looks on with a loving, comically amazed expression, surrounded by floating hearts. The scene is rendered in a flat 2D style with bold outlines, Ben-Day dots for shading, and a bright, saturated color palette of pink, yellow, and cyan. In the center, between the panels, the text "Happy Birthday to my Super-Cute Lao Lao!" is written in a beautiful, readable, bold handwritten cursive script.
